name: The 6th International Conference on Computer Science, Engineering, and Education
content: Publication: Submitted papers will go through a rigorous peer review process, and finally accepted papers after registration and presentation will be published in the CSEE 2025 conference proceedings and submitted to IEEE Xplore and possible indexing by Ei Compendex and Scopus.
